| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1683 — Recovery Inhibition (la_piovra)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e070186-088b-5532-9a49-507a97c39a95"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
